---
import RegionSection from "./RegionSection.astro";
---

<RegionSection

    title="Government"

    subtitle="Independent kingdoms united by geography, not rule."

>

<div class="government-layout">

    <div class="government-card">

        <h3>

            Independent Monarchies

        </h3>

        <p>

            Solmara is not governed by a single crown. Instead, the region
            consists of numerous independent kingdoms, each ruled by its own
            royal family, laws, and traditions.

        </p>

    </div>

    <div class="government-card">

        <h3>

            Village Representation

        </h3>

        <p>

            Every village elects a representative to present the needs of
            its people before their kingdom, ensuring every community has
            a voice regardless of size.

        </p>

    </div>

    <div class="government-card">

        <h3>

            Regional Stewardship

        </h3>

        <p>

            Elowen Waslow watches over the kingdoms as Solmara's Specter,
            preserving peace and balance while never interfering with the
            sovereignty of individual monarchies.

        </p>

    </div>

</div>

</RegionSection>

<style>

.government-layout{

    display:grid;

    grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);

    gap:2rem;

}

.government-card{

    padding:2.5rem;

    border-radius:22px;

    border:1px solid rgba(198,166,107,.15);

    background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);

    transition:.35s;

}

.government-card:hover{

    transform:translateY(-8px);

    border-color:var(--primary);

}

.government-card h3{

    font-family:"Cinzel",serif;

    margin-bottom:1rem;

}

.government-card p{

    color:var(--muted);

    line-height:1.9;

}

@media(max-width:900px){

.government-layout{

    grid-template-columns:1fr;

}

}

</style>